  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Sinus-node dysfunction or bradycardia due to advanced atrioventricular block

          -  Paced QRS duration ≥185 ms

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Left ventricular ejection fraction &lt; 50 %

          -  Acute coronary syndrome

          -  If they had undergone percutaneous coronary intervention or coronary-artery bypass
             surgery within the previous 3 months

          -  if they had a life expectancy of less than 1 year

          -  if they had received a heart transplant
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
